    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable daily driver or a solid base for a project. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the hood, and minor rust spots around the wheel wells. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few stains, though all essential electronics and controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it would benefit from a comprehensive tune-up and some suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car at an honest price for those willing to put in a little work.",
