    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this ride is. It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
