    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S, a definitive example of the 997.1 generation in museum-grade condition. This specimen is powered by the 3.8L M97.01 naturally aspirated flat-six, featuring an optimal compression ratio and a broad torque curve. The 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a factory-optioned limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. This vehicle is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), maintaining perfect damping rates with no signs of hydraulic fatigue. The cooling system has been pressure-tested, and the bores remain pristine with no scoring. Every bushing and ball joint remains at factory-spec stiffness, ensuring the communicative steering feel these cars are known for. The undercarriage is clinically clean, showing zero fluid seepage or oxidation. This is a turn-key investment for a collector demanding mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
